# Hostel Management Website

## Project Description
This project aims to develop a smart hostel management website that helps students book accommodation easily and allows the university to manage hostel rooms efficiently.

## Features
- Online room booking
- Student authentication using student ID
- stuent can book room using his matric card
- Linking the university,student , and the hotel

